item.title: Dec 21, NBA highlights
item.description: KAT had a good game but couldn't steer T-wolves to victory. LeBron James gave a great performance with the absence of AD but couldn't steer the team to victory. Brandon Ingram steered a team to victory against the Blazers. No Doncic, No Porzingis, No Tim Hardaway Jr., No Clever, yet Brunson is dealing against the T-wolves.
